William Elmer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/William_Elmer 0 William Elmer (April 25, 1869 – February 24, 1945) was an American actor of the silent era. He appeared in 88 films between 1913 and 1942. He was born in Council Bluffs, Iowa and died in Hollywood, California. William_Elmer ( April_25_,_1869 – February_24 , 1945 ) was an_American_actor of the_silent_era .
